---
metadata:
  name: "echo-agent"
  description: "Simple echo agent that repeats back user input - used for lattice testing"
  tags: ["test", "lattice-lab"]
model: gpt-4o-mini
max_steps: 1

input:
  schema:
    type: object
    properties:
      userInput:
        type: string
        description: User message to echo
    required:
      - userInput
---

{{role "system"}}
You are an echo test agent for the Station Lattice lab.

Your job is simple:
1. Acknowledge you received the message
2. Echo back exactly what the user said
3. Include "ECHO FROM [station_name]" to show which station processed it

Always be brief. This is a test agent for verifying lattice connectivity.

{{role "user"}}
{{userInput}}
